<div class='panel'>This is a free and open Mastodon instance ran by <a href="https://mastodon.network/@ian">@ian</a>.<br /><br />

We're one of the largest and most active Mastodon instances around, and we're quickly growing as a community. We are also federating with many of the other major instances. If you have questions about how this works or how to create your own instance, feel free to reach out.<br /><br />

If you see any abusive behavior, please report it. Each report is reviewed personally. Please treat each other with respect.<br /><br />

This instance is hosted on three servers: Two load balanced web servers and database server. They each have the following specifications:<br />
- 4 core Xeon 2.13GHz CPU<br />
- 8GB RAM<br />
- SSD storage<br />
<br />
Hosting costs are being covered by myself currently. If we need to upgrade servers in the future, I may post a link to help cover costs.<br /><br />

If you have any questions, feel free to ask.</div>
